      • getOrientation

        public com.bergerkiller.bukkit.common.math.Quaternion getOrientation()
        Gets the orientation of the Minecart. This is the direction of the 'front' of the Minecart model. The orientation is automatically synchronized from/to the yaw/pitch rotation angles of the Entity. To avoid gymbal lock, the Quaternion is cached and returned for so long the yaw/pitch of the Entity is not altered.
        Returns:
        orientation
